title: Olympics flame to Althorp, Northampton
cleanContent:
Children from Brington and Harlestone Primary schools are pictured together with the Earl (C) and Countess Spencer (centre R) as they welcome Fiona Warner (centre L) and the London 2012 Olympic flame to Althorp, Northampton, July 2, 2012.[Photo/Agencies]
